data.description: GREAT LOCATION…only minutes from NAS and the beautiful beaches of Perdido Key. An all-brick home with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Lovely master suite that boast 2 walk in closets in the spacious master bath. Garden tub and double vanity makes it perfect for hectic mornings. Living and Formal Dining Room on either side of foyer/ hall that leads to a family room with wood burning fireplace. Sliders open to the back yard that has enough space for an inground pool and still room for a vegetable garden. The Eat-in – Kitchen has a brand-new gas stove. Three other bedrooms share the main bath which has a tube style sky light in this split floor plan. ROOF REPLACED 2021, HVAC 2012, GAS HOT WATER HEATER JUST REPLACED Wi  Privacy fence and storage building in back yard. Great Rental potential or your forever home.
